FICO Acquires TONBELLERCombines strengths in fraud management and financial crime prevention & compliance to address expanding global market for integrated, enterprise-class, risk-based solutionsSAN JOSE, Calif. — January 13, 2015 — FICO (NYSE:FICO), the predictive analytics and decision management software company, today announced it has acquired TONBELLER, an innovative provider of financial crime and compliance solutions based in Bensheim, Germany. The transaction has closed. Although terms have not been disclosed, the transaction is not expected to have a material impact on FICO’s 2015 financial results.
